| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7881 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0dad7a5e-e8bd-58d3-884b-a39a9e880e58"
